@page "/about"

<div class="about-wrapper">
    <NavMenu />

    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="about-container">
            <div class="about-story">
                <h2 class="section-title">THE ACADEÑO STORY</h2>
                <div class="accent-bar"></div>
                
                <p class="brand-intro">
                    <strong>Acadeño is the digital sanctuary for modern students,</strong> 
                    built to turn chaotic schedules into structured, aesthetic, and actionable success.
                </p>

                <p class="brand-body">
                    We believe that academic achievement shouldn't come at the cost of your peace of mind. By merging intuitive UI design with powerful study tools, we bridge the gap between heavy course loads and the clarity required to excel. Whether you are tracking grades, managing your timetable, or finding focus in the midst of deadlines, Acadeño provides the structure you need.
                </p>

                <div class="brand-quote">
                    <em>More than a dashboard, Acadeño is your personal command center for academic mastery.</em>
                    <section class="core-values">
                        <h3>OUR CORE VALUES</h3>
                        <div class="values-grid">
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <h4>Clarity</h4>
                                <p>We strip away the complexity of academic administration, leaving you with a clear path to your goals.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <h4>Focus</h4>
                                <p>Our tools are designed to minimize distraction, helping you channel your energy into deep, productive work.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <h4>Growth</h4>
                                <p>We believe in the power of data to show you how far you’ve come, motivating you to push even further.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-sidebar">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>MISSION</h3>
                    <p>To provide students with a seamless, data-driven platform that simplifies academic management and boosts daily productivity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>VISION</h3>
                    <p>To become the global standard for student dashboards, empowering learners to reach their full potential through clarity and focus.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>GOAL</h3>
                    <p>To cultivate a disciplined study habit in every user, turning academic stress into organized, sustainable progress.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>